Package: viralquantsim
Title: Simulation and Benchmarking of Internal Controls in Quantitative Pathogen Workflows
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Juan", "Monteiro da Silva", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "juan.monteiro@outlook.com")
Description: Simulates quantitative pathogen workflows that combine target and
    spike-in internal-control qPCR measurements with sequencing-derived read
    counts. The package benchmarks when internal-control normalisation improves,
    does not change, or worsens viral-load estimation. It is intended for
    methodological research, teaching, assay design, and software demonstration,
    not clinical decision-making.
